<% content_for :title, "Download & Installation" %>
clusteval is separated into backend and frontend. The backend calculates all the clusterings and performs all the actual analyses of the framework. The frontend includes this website and a corresponding database and is responsible for the representation of the results.

<h3>Backend Executables (Client & Server)</h3>
The backend consists of a client and a server component. Both can be downloaded separately as a jar-executable.
